WEBVTT

00:01:31.100 --> 00:01:34.980
=Wonder Wall=

00:01:35.020 --> 00:01:37.910
=Episode 19=

00:01:42.439 --> 00:01:42.959
Dad,

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:44.159
how did you get here?

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:46.560
The surgery isn't over?

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:47.920
What did the doctor say?

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.840
The doctor said it wasn't serious.

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:51.239
Your mom is such a nice person.

00:01:51.599 --> 00:01:52.439
She'll be fine.

00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:54.680
Yu Ming just called me.

00:01:54.719 --> 00:01:55.319
Wenwen's been found.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.000
Yes.

00:01:56.040 --> 00:01:56.920
Wenwen's mostly fine.

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:57.680
Just a twisted ankle.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:59.040
And there are some minor scrapes.

00:01:59.159 --> 00:02:00.239
Kids heal fast.

00:02:00.319 --> 00:02:01.200
Don't worry.

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:02.200
So many of us

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:02.959
are here.

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.040
Lanying needs you.

00:02:04.079 --> 00:02:05.079
Don't keep running back here.

00:02:08.599 --> 00:02:09.039
Hello.

00:02:09.639 --> 00:02:10.479
Is this Sun Lanying's family?

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:11.560
Yes.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:12.759
Her blood pressure

00:02:12.759 --> 00:02:13.639
suddenly spiked.

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:15.039
She's had projectile vomiting.

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:16.159
Please come quickly.

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:17.360
What happened?

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.240
Doctor, how is she?

00:02:24.319 --> 00:02:25.759
She has a minor fracture in her calf

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.240
and some minor scrapes.

00:02:27.479 --> 00:02:28.159
All taken care of.

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:28.759
Thank you.

00:02:28.879 --> 00:02:29.360
Does it hurt?

00:02:29.439 --> 00:02:30.039
No.

00:02:30.159 --> 00:02:31.000
It'll heal.

00:02:33.159 --> 00:02:34.479
Maybe you should go see Du Lei.

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:35.120
Yes.

00:02:35.120 --> 00:02:35.520
Okay.

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:35.960
Keep in touch.

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:36.520
We'll take her mom.

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:37.080
Alright.

00:02:37.159 --> 00:02:37.879
Be careful.

00:02:37.879 --> 00:02:38.400
Okay.

00:02:41.908 --> 00:02:44.194
(In Operation)

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:53.240
Mom.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:54.560
Wenwen.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:55.680
She's fine.

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:56.680
Just a minor fracture in her calf

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:57.840
and some minor scrapes.

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:58.199
Is

00:02:58.240 --> 00:02:59.319
your mom not out yet?

00:02:59.439 --> 00:03:00.039
No.

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:01.199
The doctor said it wasn't serious.

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:02.159
Your dad came just now.

00:03:02.159 --> 00:03:02.879
He received a call.

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.199
Your mom might not be well.

00:03:04.199 --> 00:03:04.800
You should go.

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:05.319
Give it to me.

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:07.000
What happened to her?

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:09.120
I couldn't hear. Just go!

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:09.599
Alright.

00:03:10.639 --> 00:03:11.080
Wenwen,

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:12.639
are you hungry? Want something to eat?

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:13.360
Fried chicken.

00:03:13.759 --> 00:03:14.560
You want fried chicken?

00:03:15.199 --> 00:03:16.039
I'll go buy you some.

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:17.159
I'll go get her some.

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:17.520
Okay.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:28.639
Let me see your face.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.120
Any other injuries?

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.159
No.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.199
Don't put your hand here.

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:34.919
These are bandaged?

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:36.960
It's fine.

00:03:37.479 --> 00:03:38.080
Does it hurt?

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:39.639
No.

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:42.840
Good, you're pretty tough.

00:03:45.719 --> 00:03:47.199
I was just saving my dad's face.

00:03:47.879 --> 00:03:48.719
Didn't you say

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:50.120
if I live, he lives?

00:03:50.439 --> 00:03:51.800
If I'm strong, he's strong?

00:03:52.039 --> 00:03:52.680
I did say that.

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.240
You have good memory.

00:03:59.080 --> 00:03:59.599
Mom,

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.120
you don't blame me?

00:04:02.599 --> 00:04:03.280
Blame you for what?

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:05.159
Grandma got hurt saving me.

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:11.879
These days,

00:04:12.840 --> 00:04:13.800
I've been blaming myself.

00:04:14.759 --> 00:04:16.240
But you and Grandma both came back safe.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:17.879
I don't blame anyone anymore.

00:04:19.319 --> 00:04:20.560
It's over. It's okay.

00:04:22.399 --> 00:04:22.959
It's okay.

00:04:24.279 --> 00:04:25.279
You wanted to spend

00:04:25.319 --> 00:04:26.759
over 1,000 to get your grandma a perm.

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:28.680
Get one for me too.

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:30.360
I also need it.

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:32.839
Mom,

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:34.879
I'm a minor,

00:04:34.959 --> 00:04:36.000
and I'm already in debt

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:37.759
to Grandma for 1,000.

00:04:38.519 --> 00:04:39.720
What happened

00:04:39.839 --> 00:04:41.079
to your usual

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:42.000
upright image?

00:04:42.120 --> 00:04:43.639
Why are you so small-minded?

00:04:44.439 --> 00:04:44.959
That's fair.

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:46.759
Give your dad a perm instead.

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:51.560
Yu Wenwen,

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:54.000
I can't lose you.

00:04:55.399 --> 00:04:56.439
Don't forget me.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:58.639
Mom.

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:02.199
Stop crying.

00:05:04.623 --> 00:05:06.037
(In Operation)

00:05:20.840 --> 00:05:23.517
(Resuscitation Room)

00:05:25.639 --> 00:05:26.040
Doctor,

00:05:26.079 --> 00:05:26.920
how is she doing?

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:28.560
She's out of danger.

00:05:29.079 --> 00:05:30.160
But this time,

00:05:30.199 --> 00:05:32.199
she's had a hemorrhagic stroke.

00:05:32.439 --> 00:05:33.639
The hematoma is causing

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:34.879
a mass effect.

00:05:34.959 --> 00:05:35.879
The pressure is compressing

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:37.079
her brain tissue.

00:05:37.279 --> 00:05:38.160
So the damage

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:38.920
has already occurred.

00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:40.399
Once the nervous system

00:05:40.519 --> 00:05:41.480
is damaged,

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:43.240
recovery is very slow

00:05:43.519 --> 00:05:44.680
and unpredictable.

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:46.120
As her family,

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:47.439
you need to

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:48.519
follow the treatment,

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:49.839
and prepare for a long road ahead.

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.560
You should have confidence

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:52.480
as well as patience.

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:53.920
And please, don't do anything

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:54.879
to upset her emotionally.

00:05:55.079 --> 00:05:55.560
I understand.

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:56.240
Thank you.

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:56.639
No problem.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.639
Something happened to Mr. Yu's family.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:03.759
We should go see them.

00:06:03.839 --> 00:06:04.680
Go see Mr. Yu.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:06.120
This is the fish I dried.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:09.720
At least, send something over.

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:11.800
Mr. Yu's been through
something terrible.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:13.079
This is a copper coin sword

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:14.360
passed down in our family.

00:06:14.519 --> 00:06:15.680
Take it to Mr. Yu.

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:16.519
It'll protect him.

00:06:16.519 --> 00:06:16.839
Okay.

00:06:16.959 --> 00:06:18.040
Alright, we're going now.

00:06:18.079 --> 00:06:18.560
Let's go.

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:19.920
Don't bring that. Let's go.

00:06:19.959 --> 00:06:20.759
We're leaving.

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:22.519
We're leaving. Go.

00:06:23.480 --> 00:06:23.959
Okay.

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:25.879
Send our regards to Mr. Yu.

00:06:26.480 --> 00:06:27.600
We're leaving.

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:29.480
Drive safe.

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:48.399
Dad,

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:49.519
maybe you should go

00:06:49.519 --> 00:06:50.040
check on Mom.

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:52.360
Grandpa and I will manage here.

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:56.360
Good girl, you're so sweet.

00:06:56.600 --> 00:06:57.639
You're worried about her, right?

00:06:58.879 --> 00:06:59.519
Alright then.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:00.879
Dad,

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:02.759
I'll go check on Yitong.

00:07:02.839 --> 00:07:04.279
If everything is fine, I'll come back.

00:07:04.480 --> 00:07:05.720
You should get some sleep.

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:06.720
Why do you just sit there?

00:07:06.759 --> 00:07:07.759
There are two beds here.

00:07:07.879 --> 00:07:08.680
Just lie down

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:10.040
and get some sleep, okay?

00:07:11.519 --> 00:07:12.839
When Grandma wakes up,

00:07:12.879 --> 00:07:14.399
don't let her get too worked up.

00:07:14.759 --> 00:07:16.079
It's bad for her.

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:17.639
I'm leaving.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:37.360
She fell asleep.

00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:39.319
How is your mom?

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:40.920
She's out of danger.

00:07:41.079 --> 00:07:41.720
She's fine,

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:42.480
but

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:43.959
she might not speak

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:44.720
for a while.

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:46.279
Can't speak?

00:07:52.439 --> 00:07:52.879
Alright.

00:07:52.879 --> 00:07:53.839
So she can't talk

00:07:53.839 --> 00:07:54.600
for now.

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:57.360
She's got a really sharp tongue,

00:07:57.680 --> 00:07:58.600
cuts everyone in sight.

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:01.279
But honestly, when she cuts others,

00:08:01.279 --> 00:08:02.120
she's also

00:08:02.759 --> 00:08:04.160
hurting herself. Getting angry.

00:08:04.839 --> 00:08:05.560
So be it.

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:07.360
Just let it be.

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:08.759
Perhaps this way,

00:08:08.759 --> 00:08:10.240
she'd be in a good mood
without getting upset,

00:08:10.399 --> 00:08:11.720
maybe she'll live even longer.

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:15.000
Maybe this is a good time

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:16.759
to see if your dad

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:17.480
can move back.

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:18.439
The two are

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:19.600
companions in old age.

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:20.759
At a time like this...

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:22.800
Right?

00:08:26.199 --> 00:08:27.800
Did Guo Li say anything to you?

00:08:30.439 --> 00:08:30.959
No.

00:09:01.080 --> 00:09:01.519
Doctor,

00:09:01.919 --> 00:09:02.919
how is Du Lei doing now?

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:03.919
His life is still in danger.

00:09:04.240 --> 00:09:04.519
Then...

00:09:17.639 --> 00:09:18.679
Have some water, Mom.

00:09:21.559 --> 00:09:22.399
Here.

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:27.080
Okay, take it slow.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:39.200
Mom,

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:41.840
I never really listened to

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:43.919
all your nagging before.

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:46.919
Now I remember it all.

00:09:47.554 --> 00:09:49.394
♪You said, don't rush♪

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:52.039
You said if I kept everything to myself,

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.240
I'd get ill.

00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:55.314
♪That cup of tea on the table♪

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:58.759
You said I always rush into things.

00:09:58.861 --> 00:10:00.200
♪Nothing much has happened♪

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:01.080
I'll get hurt.

00:10:02.034 --> 00:10:03.919
♪Nothing earth-shattering at all♪

00:10:03.919 --> 00:10:06.360
So why is it you who fell?

00:10:07.639 --> 00:10:08.960
You said you can't always

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:10.559
be there to catch me.

00:10:11.759 --> 00:10:13.679
But just knowing you're behind me,

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:16.399
when I charge forward,

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:18.559
that's enough to keep me going.

00:10:18.559 --> 00:10:20.314
♪If the umbrella's downstairs♪

00:10:20.314 --> 00:10:21.634
♪We'll just get♪

00:10:21.634 --> 00:10:22.914
♪A little wet♪

00:10:23.648 --> 00:10:26.874
♪Let's wait for the rain to stop♪

00:10:26.874 --> 00:10:29.714
♪Instead of worrying so much♪

00:10:29.714 --> 00:10:32.074
♪Maybe this time♪

00:10:32.074 --> 00:10:35.279
♪I'll learn to let go♪

00:10:35.279 --> 00:10:35.799
Ming,

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:40.080
how is your mom?

00:10:40.679 --> 00:10:41.360
She's okay.

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:42.879
Did Du Lei wake up?

00:10:43.559 --> 00:10:44.279
I asked the nurse.

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:45.320
He hasn't woken up yet.

00:10:46.159 --> 00:10:46.639
I don't know

00:10:46.639 --> 00:10:48.000
where Chen Zinuo's mom went.

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:49.519
It was my fault.

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:50.360
I shouldn't have let Zinuo

00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:51.519
go find her mom alone.

00:10:56.559 --> 00:10:57.080
It's okay.

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:58.480
The police are involved now.

00:10:58.519 --> 00:10:59.759
Don't worry.

00:10:59.759 --> 00:11:00.360
She'll be fine.

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:04.480
Did our forensics team

00:11:04.679 --> 00:11:05.799
compare

00:11:05.919 --> 00:11:06.519
these two photos?

00:11:06.519 --> 00:11:07.080
Yes.

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:08.320
It's very likely

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:09.279
they're the same person.

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:11.200
I also suspect

00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:12.720
he's the owner of Bridgeway Financial,

00:11:12.759 --> 00:11:13.200
Du Lei.

00:11:13.919 --> 00:11:14.480
Du Lei?

00:11:16.879 --> 00:11:17.279
Li Jin,

00:11:17.639 --> 00:11:18.440
Chen Zinuo's mother.

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:20.279
She appeared

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:21.559
at suspicious times

00:11:21.559 --> 00:11:22.240
and locations

00:11:22.279 --> 00:11:22.919
in these two cases.

00:11:23.399 --> 00:11:24.559
And both victims

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:25.519
had frequent contact

00:11:25.519 --> 00:11:26.360
with Li Jin.

00:11:26.559 --> 00:11:27.559
This is no coincidence.

00:11:28.679 --> 00:11:29.679
Li Jin

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:30.879
must have been involved

00:11:31.080 --> 00:11:32.200
in these two cases.

00:12:10.039 --> 00:12:10.720
You're awake.

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:12.840
Grandma.

00:12:13.519 --> 00:12:14.000
Mom.

00:12:15.159 --> 00:12:16.200
Look, I'm back.

00:12:16.399 --> 00:12:17.279
I'm in great shape.

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:18.120
I'm perfectly fine.

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:20.000
Wenwen...

00:12:23.799 --> 00:12:24.399
Grandma,

00:12:24.799 --> 00:12:26.360
don't worry about me.

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:27.919
Grandma Fan was rescued too.

00:12:28.360 --> 00:12:29.799
She broke a rib saving me,

00:12:30.039 --> 00:12:31.559
but the doctor said

00:12:31.759 --> 00:12:33.320
she'll be fine in a couple of days.

00:12:34.159 --> 00:12:35.360
You also need to follow

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:36.279
the doctor's orders too.

00:12:36.399 --> 00:12:37.840
Then you'll recover soon.

00:12:40.279 --> 00:12:41.759
Don't be sad.

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:43.639
I was wrong, mom.

00:12:43.919 --> 00:12:44.960
Don't yell at me anymore.

00:12:44.960 --> 00:12:45.600
Don't get worked up.

00:12:45.639 --> 00:12:46.759
You can't get upset right now.

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:51.759
Clothes?

00:12:52.519 --> 00:12:53.159
My clothes?

00:12:53.879 --> 00:12:54.320
They stink?

00:12:56.759 --> 00:12:57.519
Your clothes?

00:12:58.200 --> 00:12:59.799
You need a change of clothes?

00:13:01.159 --> 00:13:02.519
You want me to go home

00:13:02.519 --> 00:13:03.200
and get them?

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:05.720
But you need to wear
the hospital gown here.

00:13:05.759 --> 00:13:06.759
Bringing your own won't help.

00:13:08.159 --> 00:13:08.720
Ming.

00:13:08.799 --> 00:13:09.480
Don't be anxious.

00:13:09.519 --> 00:13:10.039
Ming,

00:13:11.679 --> 00:13:12.639
your mom misses home.

00:13:12.919 --> 00:13:13.799
She wants to go home soon.

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:16.519
Okay.

00:13:16.879 --> 00:13:18.919
I'll go get your clothes ready.

00:13:19.399 --> 00:13:19.720
Okay.

00:13:19.720 --> 00:13:20.840
I'll go back to get them for you.

00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:22.320
Dad, you...

00:13:22.399 --> 00:13:23.159
You watch over mom.

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:23.600
Okay.

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:24.399
Be good, Wenwen.

00:13:24.519 --> 00:13:25.480
I'll be back soon.

00:13:25.720 --> 00:13:26.360
Okay.

00:13:37.919 --> 00:13:38.480
Don't worry.

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:39.720
Don't get upset.

00:13:39.879 --> 00:13:40.720
Stay calm.

00:14:02.830 --> 00:14:06.065
(New Character Workbook,
Class 7, Grade 4, Yu Feng)

00:14:41.980 --> 00:14:44.404
(Demo for Mr. Money,
Recorded on 2011.7.21, Yu Ming)

00:15:00.720 --> 00:15:01.120
Mom.

00:15:02.080 --> 00:15:02.559
Mom,

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:04.799
I finished my new song.

00:15:05.159 --> 00:15:06.120
Do you want to hear it?

00:15:07.919 --> 00:15:09.120
You recorded it with your own money.

00:15:09.120 --> 00:15:10.039
What's so impressive about it?

00:15:10.559 --> 00:15:11.960
Everything your brother earns,

00:15:12.080 --> 00:15:13.440
goes straight to you.

00:15:14.240 --> 00:15:15.000
Good-for-nothing.

00:15:15.314 --> 00:15:17.480
♪Where have you gone?♪

00:15:17.514 --> 00:15:19.320
(Demo for Mr. Money,
Recorded on 2011.7.21, Yu Ming)

00:15:19.320 --> 00:15:21.320
It's really good.

00:15:21.320 --> 00:15:21.720
Really?

00:15:23.159 --> 00:15:23.759
Let me tell you,

00:15:24.399 --> 00:15:25.639
this is the best song

00:15:25.679 --> 00:15:27.159
you've ever made.

00:15:27.759 --> 00:15:29.000
It'll be a hit if you issue an album.

00:15:29.000 --> 00:15:30.985
♪To those who pass me by♪

00:15:32.465 --> 00:15:35.280
♪You don't have to look at me♪

00:15:36.732 --> 00:15:40.046
♪Just keep walking your own way♪

00:15:41.011 --> 00:15:43.280
♪I'll manage on my own♪

00:15:46.907 --> 00:15:50.320
♪Is the rain falling hard♪

00:15:51.879 --> 00:15:52.559
Turns out

00:15:53.320 --> 00:15:54.480
you kept the song I wrote

00:15:55.639 --> 00:15:58.159
right next to you.

00:15:59.399 --> 00:15:59.919
Mom,

00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:01.720
I thought

00:16:02.440 --> 00:16:04.799
all you ever had for me
was disappointment.

00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:06.799
Now I finally understand

00:16:07.519 --> 00:16:08.960
the love and pain

00:16:09.559 --> 00:16:12.240
you hid inside.

00:16:13.440 --> 00:16:14.840
Sorry, Mom.

00:16:15.840 --> 00:16:18.720
I realized too late.

00:16:20.080 --> 00:16:21.519
Am I not your own son?

00:16:21.519 --> 00:16:22.759
Did you pick me up somewhere?

00:16:23.159 --> 00:16:24.799
I've been trying very hard.

00:16:25.080 --> 00:16:26.919
I had no choice, mom.

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:28.840
I want to be as excellent

00:16:28.840 --> 00:16:29.879
as my brother.

00:16:30.159 --> 00:16:31.559
But fate and you

00:16:31.799 --> 00:16:33.360
just can't see me.

00:16:33.639 --> 00:16:34.840
What can I do?

00:16:38.808 --> 00:16:42.043
♪The road ahead is still so long♪

00:16:43.121 --> 00:16:45.545
♪Where have you gone♪

00:16:47.306 --> 00:16:49.891
♪Under the blazing sun♪

00:16:51.645 --> 00:16:53.811
♪I keep heading north♪

00:16:55.970 --> 00:16:58.966
♪To those who pass me by♪

00:17:00.559 --> 00:17:01.159
Bigfoot,

00:17:01.480 --> 00:17:02.799
I'm feeding the chicken,

00:17:02.840 --> 00:17:03.159
packing up

00:17:03.159 --> 00:17:04.519
my parents' clothes

00:17:04.519 --> 00:17:06.400
Take them to the hospital.

00:17:06.559 --> 00:17:08.559
Then drop Wenwen off at school.

00:17:08.759 --> 00:17:10.440
After that, I'll go find you.

00:17:10.440 --> 00:17:11.359
Are you...

00:17:11.519 --> 00:17:12.319
Are you at the station?

00:17:12.680 --> 00:17:13.319
I'm outside now.

00:17:13.319 --> 00:17:14.319
I can't get back for a while.

00:17:15.400 --> 00:17:16.039
Okay then.

00:17:16.039 --> 00:17:17.400
I'll go back to Ziyu Garden.

00:17:17.440 --> 00:17:18.400
I need to change the password.

00:17:18.519 --> 00:17:18.920
You can just

00:17:19.079 --> 00:17:20.279
pick me up

00:17:20.319 --> 00:17:21.079
on your way.

00:17:21.440 --> 00:17:22.000
Okay then.

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:22.960
Wait for me at Unit 505.

00:17:23.920 --> 00:17:24.400
I got to go.

00:17:24.440 --> 00:17:25.079
Another call.

00:17:26.960 --> 00:17:27.319
Captain Guo,

00:17:27.559 --> 00:17:29.079
today we found a hidden camera

00:17:29.079 --> 00:17:30.039
inside an air conditioning unit

00:17:30.039 --> 00:17:30.759
at Du Lei's office.

00:17:30.880 --> 00:17:31.640
It's confirmed that Li Jin

00:17:31.680 --> 00:17:32.519
took Chen Zinuo.

00:17:32.759 --> 00:17:33.839
Quickly check all the cameras

00:17:33.839 --> 00:17:34.880
near Du Lei's company.

00:17:35.119 --> 00:17:36.279
Find Li Jin's location now.

00:18:14.400 --> 00:18:16.559
Jiajia is picking you up tonight.

00:18:16.960 --> 00:18:17.920
Your mom already told her.

00:18:17.960 --> 00:18:18.680
In the next few days,

00:18:19.079 --> 00:18:19.920
you'll stay

00:18:19.920 --> 00:18:20.640
with her.

00:18:21.160 --> 00:18:22.400
And at her place,

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:23.599
don't act spoiled

00:18:23.599 --> 00:18:24.519
like you do at home.

00:18:24.519 --> 00:18:26.000
Listen to Jiajia,

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:26.400
Okay?

00:18:26.759 --> 00:18:27.799
Don't worry so much.

00:18:27.839 --> 00:18:28.960
I'm quite happy staying at her place.

00:18:29.480 --> 00:18:30.000
It's big.

00:18:30.200 --> 00:18:31.200
I can have enough space

00:18:31.200 --> 00:18:32.160
to move around.

00:18:32.799 --> 00:18:34.160
Wenwen.

00:18:34.440 --> 00:18:35.000
You got injured?

00:18:35.680 --> 00:18:36.480
How could I not be injured

00:18:36.559 --> 00:18:37.519
from a narrow escape?

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:40.000
Her foot's not good right now.

00:18:40.039 --> 00:18:41.480
Look out for her at school.

00:18:41.680 --> 00:18:42.000
Okay.

00:18:42.240 --> 00:18:43.160
No problem.

00:18:43.160 --> 00:18:43.519
Thank you.

00:19:05.039 --> 00:19:06.200
When your little red car

00:19:06.880 --> 00:19:08.079
fancies another good-looking car,

00:19:08.119 --> 00:19:09.400
suddenly she's got no self-control?

00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:11.759
Your car is just too attractive.

00:19:11.799 --> 00:19:12.960
It keeps seducing mine.

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:15.759
Currently,

00:19:16.279 --> 00:19:17.960
I have no time to fix your car for you.

00:19:18.039 --> 00:19:19.200
What are you saying?

00:19:19.319 --> 00:19:20.519
What's our relationship?

00:19:21.039 --> 00:19:21.920
Use your insurance.

00:19:23.519 --> 00:19:24.480
Let me tell you.

00:19:24.680 --> 00:19:25.920
I found this

00:19:26.039 --> 00:19:27.440
MBA swimming class.

00:19:27.880 --> 00:19:29.000
Whole family thing. Really fun.

00:19:29.039 --> 00:19:30.079
I'll sign your family up too.

00:19:30.240 --> 00:19:31.519
Then wait for me to go with you.

00:19:31.559 --> 00:19:32.079
Get some practice.

00:19:32.319 --> 00:19:33.279
You can teach me

00:19:33.279 --> 00:19:34.119
your freestyle,

00:19:34.279 --> 00:19:35.160
that awesome one.

00:19:35.599 --> 00:19:36.880
Won't your daughter's legs

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:38.359
need some rehab training?

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:39.200
She can do butterfly.

00:19:39.599 --> 00:19:40.480
But I don't think your wife

00:19:40.519 --> 00:19:41.279
should go in the water.

00:19:41.559 --> 00:19:42.720
She talks too much.

00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:43.920
She'd swallow water.

00:19:44.200 --> 00:19:44.599
Right?

00:20:05.440 --> 00:20:06.079
Which way is it?

00:20:08.759 --> 00:20:09.200
Missed it.

00:20:10.240 --> 00:20:10.880
What's going on?

00:20:10.880 --> 00:20:11.400
It froze.

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:12.279
My phone froze.

00:20:12.319 --> 00:20:13.279
You bought a used box truck,

00:20:13.279 --> 00:20:14.759
and you buy used phones too?

00:20:14.839 --> 00:20:15.440
Your phone's junk.

00:20:15.440 --> 00:20:17.079
Use the old clunker. Ask Great-Grandma.

00:20:17.480 --> 00:20:17.920
Yeah.

00:20:20.079 --> 00:20:21.039
Don't touch my gear shift.

00:20:24.519 --> 00:20:25.440
200 meters ahead,

00:20:25.799 --> 00:20:26.319
turn right.

00:20:26.440 --> 00:20:27.200
There is a gas station.

00:20:27.480 --> 00:20:28.720
Zhu, I need to pee.

00:20:54.519 --> 00:20:55.200
Take it easy.

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:56.559
I can't hold it.

00:20:56.839 --> 00:20:57.519
Get some water too.

00:21:30.799 --> 00:21:31.240
Chui,

00:21:31.480 --> 00:21:33.160
I could barely keep my eyes on the GPS.

00:21:33.680 --> 00:21:34.400
I was really sleepy.

00:21:35.279 --> 00:21:36.319
You can't fall asleep.

00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:37.759
There's still a long way to go.

00:21:37.839 --> 00:21:38.599
We need to keep moving.

00:21:38.880 --> 00:21:39.240
Okay.

00:21:40.559 --> 00:21:40.960
Chui,

00:21:41.519 --> 00:21:42.400
maybe you should drive.

00:21:43.039 --> 00:21:44.119
Zhu can't go on either.

00:21:44.359 --> 00:21:45.119
You slept all the way here.

00:21:45.519 --> 00:21:46.680
When was I sleeping?

00:21:47.119 --> 00:21:48.079
I'll drive.

00:21:48.160 --> 00:21:49.039
You hurry up.

00:21:49.519 --> 00:21:49.960
I...

00:21:50.079 --> 00:21:51.279
I'm done.

00:21:51.319 --> 00:21:52.440
I'm waiting for you.

00:21:52.720 --> 00:21:53.599
You hurry up and leave.

00:21:54.000 --> 00:21:55.279
How could I pee when you're watching me?

00:21:55.279 --> 00:21:56.720
Hurry up. Don't waste time.

00:21:56.799 --> 00:21:57.680
Dawdling there.

00:21:57.680 --> 00:21:59.079
You're so fussy.

00:22:12.400 --> 00:22:13.880
Well, this one, this one,

00:22:15.039 --> 00:22:15.400
and this.

00:22:15.559 --> 00:22:16.119
Three orders.

00:22:16.640 --> 00:22:16.920
Sure.

00:22:17.119 --> 00:22:17.440
To go.

00:22:18.119 --> 00:22:19.039
Extra rice.

00:22:19.079 --> 00:22:19.400
Okay.

00:22:42.359 --> 00:22:42.799
Where is he?

00:23:12.839 --> 00:23:13.400
Sorry,

00:23:13.680 --> 00:23:14.960
my daughter's allergic to mangoes.

00:23:15.039 --> 00:23:15.359
Switch it.

00:23:15.599 --> 00:23:15.920
Okay.

00:23:20.680 --> 00:23:21.200
How much?

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:23.000
Let me scan.

00:23:24.119 --> 00:23:24.640
Thank you.

00:23:31.759 --> 00:23:32.039
Take care.

00:23:35.160 --> 00:23:35.599
Zhu.

00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:39.559
Let me drive.

00:23:39.599 --> 00:23:41.160
You look so sleepy.

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:42.519
Give me the key.

00:23:53.240 --> 00:23:53.640
Zhu,

00:23:54.599 --> 00:23:55.519
why does the truck

00:23:55.519 --> 00:23:56.440
feel different now?

00:23:56.960 --> 00:23:57.880
You're just sleepy.

00:23:58.400 --> 00:23:59.440
What's that scent?

00:23:59.759 --> 00:24:00.680
Stop talking.

00:24:01.359 --> 00:24:02.240
Just focus on driving.

00:24:03.759 --> 00:24:04.359
Keep the change.

00:24:21.400 --> 00:24:21.920
Yu Ming,

00:24:22.240 --> 00:24:23.119
why did you ask me to come?

00:24:26.200 --> 00:24:28.359
Just come in first.

00:24:35.240 --> 00:24:35.799
So,

00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:37.759
the 30 million found in the wall

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:39.799
belonged
to property developer Hu Deshuai.

00:24:40.319 --> 00:24:41.400
As for the 30 million

00:24:41.640 --> 00:24:43.359
in the basement,

00:24:43.759 --> 00:24:47.079
it belonged to Chen Liyang,

00:24:47.279 --> 00:24:48.240
the previous owner.

00:24:48.839 --> 00:24:50.400
What about
the three construction workers?

00:24:50.440 --> 00:24:52.079
They dug up that 30 million.

00:24:52.640 --> 00:24:53.200
But

00:24:53.400 --> 00:24:54.640
they're not greedy.

00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:56.359
They only wanted

00:24:56.720 --> 00:24:57.640
two million

00:24:57.680 --> 00:24:58.799
that Hu Deshuai owed them.

00:24:59.559 --> 00:25:01.039
I acted on my own
So I went ahead and

00:25:01.200 --> 00:25:02.440
and gave them two million.

00:25:02.680 --> 00:25:04.039
They've put their signatures

00:25:04.359 --> 00:25:05.279
and fingerprints on it.

00:25:05.480 --> 00:25:06.359
I have the evidence.

00:25:06.599 --> 00:25:08.119
There was a total of 60 million.

00:25:08.599 --> 00:25:10.160
I gave them two million,

00:25:10.279 --> 00:25:12.119
so there was 58 million left.

00:25:12.400 --> 00:25:13.759
However, this 58 million

00:25:13.920 --> 00:25:15.200
has all been scammed away

00:25:15.279 --> 00:25:16.160
by Chen Zinuo's mother.

00:25:16.359 --> 00:25:17.559
Jiang Juan and Zhan Chun,

00:25:17.680 --> 00:25:18.640
who kidnapped Wenwen

00:25:18.759 --> 00:25:20.240
and my mother-in-law,

00:25:20.319 --> 00:25:21.119
were after

00:25:21.119 --> 00:25:22.759
Hu Deshuai's 30 million

00:25:22.799 --> 00:25:24.599
in the wall.

00:25:24.759 --> 00:25:25.519
They didn't know

00:25:25.599 --> 00:25:26.599
there was 60 million here.

00:25:26.880 --> 00:25:27.440
I don't know

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:28.559
if I've made myself clear.

00:25:29.960 --> 00:25:30.640
It's clear.

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:33.680
I remember you being

00:25:33.720 --> 00:25:34.599
a pretty timid guy.

00:25:35.039 --> 00:25:35.759
Something this big,

00:25:35.759 --> 00:25:36.519
and you held on that long?

00:25:36.920 --> 00:25:37.559
Pretty impressive.

00:25:37.960 --> 00:25:39.160
Did it never cross your mind

00:25:39.240 --> 00:25:40.480
that if that 60 million was clean,

00:25:40.559 --> 00:25:41.480
why would someone wall it up

00:25:41.519 --> 00:25:42.160
or bury it underground?

00:25:42.680 --> 00:25:43.519
Now 60 million

00:25:43.599 --> 00:25:44.640
down to 58.

00:25:44.759 --> 00:25:45.519
That's definitely

00:25:45.519 --> 00:25:46.319
illegal possession.

00:25:46.519 --> 00:25:47.240
What was on your mind?

00:25:48.240 --> 00:25:49.359
Why didn't you turn yourself in?

00:25:49.559 --> 00:25:51.119
I thought about it and I even tried.

00:25:51.240 --> 00:25:52.400
Yitong went with me.

00:25:52.440 --> 00:25:53.480
She asked me to turn myself in.

00:25:53.519 --> 00:25:54.480
We went to see you.

00:25:54.559 --> 00:25:55.440
Do you remember it?

00:25:55.480 --> 00:25:57.839
But then I ran away.

00:25:58.759 --> 00:25:59.480
Why did you run away?

00:25:59.920 --> 00:26:01.079
Well, on that day, we got

00:26:01.079 --> 00:26:01.920
everything ready.

00:26:01.960 --> 00:26:02.920
I wrote a letter about everything

00:26:02.960 --> 00:26:03.799
to my family.

00:26:03.799 --> 00:26:04.599
I had it all laid out.

00:26:04.599 --> 00:26:05.359
I planned

00:26:05.400 --> 00:26:07.319
to turn myself in and hand in the money.

00:26:07.400 --> 00:26:08.759
I'll accept any punishment.

00:26:08.839 --> 00:26:10.240
But when I was on my way,

00:26:10.319 --> 00:26:11.400
someone beside me

00:26:11.599 --> 00:26:12.240
mentioned a guy

00:26:12.279 --> 00:26:13.119
that rotted in prison

00:26:13.119 --> 00:26:14.039
because of just 5 million.

00:26:14.039 --> 00:26:14.799
Then I thought of mine.

00:26:14.839 --> 00:26:15.680
It scared me to death.

00:26:15.720 --> 00:26:17.039
Running was out of instinct.

00:26:17.839 --> 00:26:18.480
You've just

00:26:18.480 --> 00:26:19.680
dug up your own grave.

00:26:22.799 --> 00:26:24.079
Bigfoot, here's the thing.

00:26:24.240 --> 00:26:24.960
Yitong and I

00:26:25.079 --> 00:26:25.759
never spent a penny

00:26:25.799 --> 00:26:26.839
of this 60 million.

00:26:26.839 --> 00:26:27.480
And to be honest,

00:26:27.640 --> 00:26:28.960
Yitong doesn't know much about it.

00:26:28.960 --> 00:26:30.119
I was the one who found the money.

00:26:30.160 --> 00:26:31.119
When I told her,

00:26:31.160 --> 00:26:32.680
she kept pushing me to turn myself in.

00:26:32.920 --> 00:26:34.440
I hope this thing...

00:26:34.599 --> 00:26:35.680
In fact, this thing

00:26:35.720 --> 00:26:37.039
has nothing to do with Yitong at all.

00:26:37.200 --> 00:26:37.960
I did it all alone.

00:26:37.960 --> 00:26:38.279
Well,

00:26:38.759 --> 00:26:41.039
the fact that I'm coming clean now

00:26:41.039 --> 00:26:42.279
does that count as turning myself in?

00:26:42.279 --> 00:26:43.599
Since

00:26:43.720 --> 00:26:44.640
I turned myself in,

00:26:44.680 --> 00:26:45.440
confessing voluntarily,

00:26:45.440 --> 00:26:45.960
could I maybe

00:26:46.000 --> 00:26:47.359
get some leniency?

00:26:47.680 --> 00:26:49.000
Come back with me
to the station first.

00:26:51.720 --> 00:26:53.400
♪Work hard and make money♪

00:26:53.400 --> 00:26:54.799
♪I want to get rich♪

00:26:55.480 --> 00:26:56.960
(San)
♪A villa by the sea♪

00:26:57.200 --> 00:26:58.680
Can I take a call?

00:26:59.000 --> 00:27:00.519
Go ahead. You're not detained yet.

00:27:01.759 --> 00:27:02.119
Hello.

00:27:02.400 --> 00:27:02.880
Mr. Yu,

00:27:03.160 --> 00:27:03.720
this is San.

00:27:04.160 --> 00:27:05.119
Did you find your child?

00:27:05.559 --> 00:27:06.920
Yes. Don't worry.

00:27:07.160 --> 00:27:07.920
She's been found.

00:27:08.599 --> 00:27:09.440
She has been found.

00:27:09.920 --> 00:27:10.400
That's good.

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:10.960
Mr. Yu,

00:27:11.559 --> 00:27:12.240
we're at the door

00:27:12.240 --> 00:27:13.440
of Unit 505.

00:27:13.799 --> 00:27:14.480
Are you in the house?

00:27:15.279 --> 00:27:15.759
Yes.

00:27:16.519 --> 00:27:17.640
We brought some local specialties.

00:27:18.079 --> 00:27:19.559
Could you

00:27:19.599 --> 00:27:20.400
come out to get them?

00:27:22.359 --> 00:27:22.880
Okay.

00:27:23.279 --> 00:27:24.599
I'm coming out.

00:27:26.400 --> 00:27:27.519
The three construction works

00:27:28.160 --> 00:27:30.319
have brought me some gifts.

00:27:30.960 --> 00:27:32.000
I...

00:27:32.119 --> 00:27:32.880
Some local specialties.

00:27:33.799 --> 00:27:35.039
Please don't make me look bad.

00:27:35.039 --> 00:27:35.440
Okay?

00:27:38.720 --> 00:27:40.000
So you do have a sense of shame now.

00:27:48.319 --> 00:27:49.160
Mr. Yu.

00:27:49.160 --> 00:27:50.200
Your child has been found?

00:27:50.559 --> 00:27:51.079
Yes.

00:27:51.079 --> 00:27:51.680
Don't worry.

00:27:51.680 --> 00:27:52.640
Everyone's grateful to you.

00:27:52.720 --> 00:27:53.440
Hurry and open it.

00:27:53.880 --> 00:27:54.759
All local specialties.

00:27:55.319 --> 00:27:57.079
Chicken, ducks, fish,

00:27:57.160 --> 00:27:58.039
and all kinds of vegetables,

00:27:58.079 --> 00:27:58.880
which we grew ourselves.

00:27:58.880 --> 00:27:59.720
You're too kind.

00:28:00.759 --> 00:28:01.599
No need to do this for me.

00:28:45.680 --> 00:28:46.519
This must be the money

00:28:46.519 --> 00:28:47.559
you handed over to Li Jin.

00:28:47.880 --> 00:28:48.519
Yes.

00:28:48.680 --> 00:28:49.680
I just put the money

00:28:49.680 --> 00:28:50.920
in these suitcases

00:28:50.920 --> 00:28:53.039
and loaded them onto the box truck.

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:54.039
After that...

00:28:54.039 --> 00:28:54.519
How did the money

00:28:54.519 --> 00:28:55.559
end up back here?

00:28:57.000 --> 00:28:57.799
I don't know.

00:28:57.880 --> 00:28:59.279
You need to ask them.

00:29:01.839 --> 00:29:03.400
We came to send

00:29:03.519 --> 00:29:04.200
something to Mr. Yu.

00:29:04.240 --> 00:29:05.240
Some local specialties.

00:29:05.720 --> 00:29:07.920
About the suitcases

00:29:07.920 --> 00:29:08.440
and that girl,

00:29:08.559 --> 00:29:09.880
we really don't know

00:29:09.920 --> 00:29:11.400
how they appeared in the box.

00:29:12.119 --> 00:29:13.640
You three come with me

00:29:13.839 --> 00:29:15.200
and explain clearly

00:29:15.319 --> 00:29:15.960
this money.

00:29:16.039 --> 00:29:17.519
We really didn't kidnap her.

00:29:17.799 --> 00:29:18.160
We...

00:29:18.160 --> 00:29:19.359
we had nothing to do with that.

00:29:19.359 --> 00:29:20.200
Really.

00:29:20.200 --> 00:29:21.640
I just drove the truck here.

00:29:22.200 --> 00:29:22.839
On your way here,

00:29:22.839 --> 00:29:23.680
did you see her?

00:29:26.359 --> 00:29:27.000
This woman.

00:29:28.519 --> 00:29:29.039
No.

00:29:33.359 --> 00:29:33.920
No.

00:29:36.119 --> 00:29:36.720
Wait a second.

00:29:37.599 --> 00:29:40.359
I've seen her.

00:29:44.960 --> 00:29:45.519
Sorry,

00:29:45.799 --> 00:29:47.119
but my daughter is allergic to mangoes.

00:29:47.200 --> 00:29:47.680
Switch it.

00:29:47.799 --> 00:29:48.079
Okay.

00:29:54.559 --> 00:29:55.039
How much?

00:29:56.119 --> 00:29:56.759
Let me scan.

00:29:57.920 --> 00:29:58.440
Thank you.

00:30:07.200 --> 00:30:08.079
Our truck is here.

00:30:12.720 --> 00:30:13.319
Let me drive.

00:30:13.480 --> 00:30:14.920
You look so sleepy.

00:30:15.880 --> 00:30:16.400
Give me the key.

00:30:19.279 --> 00:30:20.200
Why does the truck

00:30:20.200 --> 00:30:21.119
feel different now?

00:30:21.640 --> 00:30:22.559
You're just sleepy.

00:30:23.079 --> 00:30:24.119
What's that scent?

00:30:45.359 --> 00:30:45.720
Here.

00:31:27.359 --> 00:31:27.759
Captain Guo.

00:31:29.079 --> 00:31:29.519
Come here.

00:31:33.799 --> 00:31:34.200
What's up?

00:31:35.039 --> 00:31:35.720
We found the suspect

00:31:35.720 --> 00:31:36.920
and the wrong box truck.

00:31:36.920 --> 00:31:37.240
Look.

00:31:37.799 --> 00:31:38.599
After driving the truck

00:31:38.720 --> 00:31:40.119
past the Chen City South Toll Station,

00:31:40.480 --> 00:31:41.519
she pulled over,

00:31:41.759 --> 00:31:42.799
got out to check the back,

00:31:43.079 --> 00:31:43.799
then turned around

00:31:43.960 --> 00:31:44.559
and drove back.

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.440
She'll return to
Pengxing Lake Service Area

00:31:46.480 --> 00:31:47.400
to find her own truck back.

00:31:47.720 --> 00:31:48.680
Contact Chen City immediately

00:31:48.839 --> 00:31:49.599
and help us take her.

00:31:49.640 --> 00:31:50.039
Captain,

00:31:50.119 --> 00:31:50.799
here's the information

00:31:50.839 --> 00:31:51.599
from Luzhou.

00:31:51.920 --> 00:31:52.759
At 4:05 p.m., the suspect

00:31:52.759 --> 00:31:53.720
arrived at the Chen City Toll Station,

00:31:53.799 --> 00:31:54.880
but turned back onto the highway.

00:31:55.240 --> 00:31:56.480
It's very likely that she'd

00:31:56.599 --> 00:31:57.799
return to Pengxing Lake Service Area.

00:31:58.759 --> 00:32:00.160
Immediately seal off the S9 northbound

00:32:00.240 --> 00:32:01.119
toll stations

00:32:01.200 --> 00:32:01.920
at Changtai and Zhaoyang.

00:32:02.319 --> 00:32:03.559
Leave only one lane

00:32:03.720 --> 00:32:05.000
Set up surveillance at all gas stations

00:32:05.200 --> 00:32:06.240
and service areas along the route.

00:32:07.000 --> 00:32:08.559
Notify our colleagues at Pengxing Lake.

00:32:08.680 --> 00:32:09.240
Tell them

00:32:09.240 --> 00:32:10.880
to watch her closely, but stay hidden.

00:32:11.880 --> 00:32:13.599
I've told you everything I know.

00:32:13.759 --> 00:32:14.440
If I hadn't been

00:32:14.440 --> 00:32:15.480
too eager to help them,

00:32:15.480 --> 00:32:16.480
I wouldn't have touched

00:32:16.480 --> 00:32:17.559
a penny of that 60 million.

00:32:17.640 --> 00:32:18.119
Why is there

00:32:18.119 --> 00:32:19.079
only 58 million left?

00:32:19.200 --> 00:32:21.640
Because Hu Deshuai owed
those three workers

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:22.759
two million in back pay.

00:32:22.839 --> 00:32:24.359
The money should be theirs.

00:32:24.400 --> 00:32:25.400
When we learned Mr. Yu's family

00:32:25.400 --> 00:32:25.839
had an accident,

00:32:25.880 --> 00:32:26.480
we just came over.

00:32:26.519 --> 00:32:27.319
The villagers found out

00:32:27.319 --> 00:32:28.480
we were going to see Mr. Yu,

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:29.480
they all came with gifts.

00:32:29.599 --> 00:32:31.119
Chicken, ducks, geese, fish,

00:32:31.240 --> 00:32:32.200
all free-range.

00:32:32.279 --> 00:32:33.319
And the homegrown vegetables.

00:32:33.319 --> 00:32:34.359
I told them we'd take no more,

00:32:34.440 --> 00:32:35.359
but they insisted.

00:32:35.400 --> 00:32:36.359
I finally said okay, enough,

00:32:36.359 --> 00:32:36.920
stop giving,

00:32:36.920 --> 00:32:37.920
but they kept stuffing things.

00:32:37.920 --> 00:32:38.480
Stop.

00:32:39.240 --> 00:32:39.960
How did you know

00:32:39.960 --> 00:32:40.920
Yu Ming's family had an accident?

00:32:41.000 --> 00:32:41.759
My great-grandma told me.

00:32:41.839 --> 00:32:43.319
She was in her room, using a stick

00:32:43.400 --> 00:32:44.079
to knock the spittoon.

00:32:44.200 --> 00:32:45.960
Once means yes, twice means no.

00:32:45.960 --> 00:32:46.519
Stop now.

00:32:46.680 --> 00:32:47.559
What about the two million?

00:32:47.559 --> 00:32:48.559
Mr. Yu

00:32:48.599 --> 00:32:49.920
gave the money to us.

00:32:50.319 --> 00:32:51.000
Is it this one?

00:32:51.359 --> 00:32:52.319
That's it.

00:32:52.440 --> 00:32:53.599
133 of us have put our thumbprints

00:32:53.599 --> 00:32:54.240
on it.

00:32:54.279 --> 00:32:55.640
Mr. Yu and his wife

00:32:55.759 --> 00:32:56.799
counted the money for us.

00:32:56.839 --> 00:32:57.799
Two million,

00:32:57.880 --> 00:32:58.880
without even blinking en eye.

00:32:59.039 --> 00:33:00.880
We even filmed it when we got paid.

00:33:00.960 --> 00:33:02.519
Everyone signed, thumbprinted.

00:33:02.519 --> 00:33:03.480
It was a happy day.

00:33:03.640 --> 00:33:04.720
I don't know how it happened,

00:33:04.720 --> 00:33:05.119
but somehow

00:33:05.119 --> 00:33:06.359
we got the wrong truck.

00:33:06.400 --> 00:33:07.880
My brother was too tired to drive,

00:33:07.880 --> 00:33:08.799
so I took over.

00:33:09.079 --> 00:33:09.920
Can we find

00:33:10.440 --> 00:33:11.559
our truck back?

00:33:12.519 --> 00:33:13.640
Your truck has been found.

00:33:14.880 --> 00:33:15.519
Thank you.

00:33:15.559 --> 00:33:16.400
Thank you.

00:33:16.920 --> 00:33:18.240
Thank you very much.

00:33:24.319 --> 00:33:26.519
Mr. Yu, can you keep this

00:33:26.720 --> 00:33:28.079
from her for now?

00:33:28.920 --> 00:33:30.640
Yitong is also keeping it

00:33:31.079 --> 00:33:32.200
from her mother.

00:33:32.400 --> 00:33:33.000
Just don't

00:33:33.480 --> 00:33:34.240
spill the beans.

00:33:35.880 --> 00:33:37.119
How long do we have to keep this?

00:33:37.400 --> 00:33:38.240
When will the police

00:33:38.799 --> 00:33:39.880
release Yu Ming

00:33:39.880 --> 00:33:41.200
after the investigation?

00:33:43.440 --> 00:33:44.359
Could he be convicted

00:33:44.359 --> 00:33:45.480
of some crime?

00:33:45.680 --> 00:33:46.480
That won't happen.

00:33:47.119 --> 00:33:48.079
I asked my parents

00:33:48.119 --> 00:33:49.160
to consult a top-notch lawyer.

00:33:49.319 --> 00:33:49.960
He said

00:33:50.079 --> 00:33:51.680
as long as Ming didn't touch the money,

00:33:51.839 --> 00:33:53.079
it's not illegal possession.

00:33:54.640 --> 00:33:55.799
Haven't they given two million

00:33:55.839 --> 00:33:56.960
to those construction workers?

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:09.719
What's the situation?

00:34:10.119 --> 00:34:11.159
The target hasn't shown up yet.

00:34:11.440 --> 00:34:12.639
But command center says

00:34:12.760 --> 00:34:14.519
the suspect's vehicle
didn't make any stops.

00:34:15.039 --> 00:34:15.559
An,

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:16.920
you block the west exit.

00:34:17.079 --> 00:34:18.079
Liu and I will block the east.

00:34:18.679 --> 00:34:19.840
Once we spot the suspect's vehicle,

00:34:19.960 --> 00:34:21.119
seal off both exits immediately.

00:34:21.280 --> 00:34:21.639
Copy that.

00:34:21.639 --> 00:34:22.199
Go!

00:35:08.119 --> 00:35:08.920
Target vehicle spotted.

00:35:30.239 --> 00:35:30.639
Seal the road!

00:35:45.760 --> 00:35:46.280
Take her!

00:36:02.480 --> 00:36:03.239
Who are you?

00:36:05.760 --> 00:36:06.719
You can't go inside!

00:36:09.880 --> 00:36:10.280
Where's she?

00:36:10.800 --> 00:36:11.199
Inside.

00:36:13.000 --> 00:36:13.559
The keys.

00:36:13.639 --> 00:36:14.800
The keys...

00:36:15.000 --> 00:36:15.480
Here.

00:36:44.480 --> 00:36:46.199
Call an ambulance, quick!

00:36:47.840 --> 00:36:49.119
All of this is over.

00:36:50.239 --> 00:36:51.440
The only one who can judge me

00:36:52.679 --> 00:36:54.239
is myself.

00:36:57.079 --> 00:36:58.440
The case investigation is clear now.

00:36:58.519 --> 00:36:59.920
This doesn't count
as illegal possession.

00:37:00.119 --> 00:37:01.880
So don't let it weigh on you.

00:37:02.119 --> 00:37:03.000
And the money

00:37:03.039 --> 00:37:03.880
has been handed in.

00:37:04.440 --> 00:37:05.920
As for the two million

00:37:06.159 --> 00:37:07.159
you gave to the workers,

00:37:07.199 --> 00:37:08.119
they'll bring it here tomorrow.

00:37:09.079 --> 00:37:09.840
Now

00:37:09.880 --> 00:37:11.679
the police have decided
not to press charges.

00:37:12.000 --> 00:37:13.360
You can go home first,

00:37:13.639 --> 00:37:14.239
but

00:37:14.440 --> 00:37:15.480
don't let it happen again.

00:37:15.519 --> 00:37:16.960
I know. It won't.

00:37:17.079 --> 00:37:17.920
It can never happen again.

00:37:17.960 --> 00:37:18.880
I was terribly scared.

00:37:18.960 --> 00:37:19.280
Yu Ming,

00:37:19.480 --> 00:37:20.400
I'll give you this,

00:37:20.599 --> 00:37:21.639
you catch on quick.

00:37:22.559 --> 00:37:23.840
Don't say that.

00:37:24.079 --> 00:37:25.639
Anyone facing such a thing would...

00:37:27.079 --> 00:37:28.800
But maybe you should reconsider
that two million

00:37:29.079 --> 00:37:30.440
for the construction workers.

00:37:30.679 --> 00:37:31.480
This should be

00:37:31.480 --> 00:37:32.239
their money.

00:37:33.000 --> 00:37:33.760
Don't worry.

00:37:34.039 --> 00:37:34.840
I've reported this

00:37:34.840 --> 00:37:35.800
to my superiors.

00:37:36.039 --> 00:37:36.599
There's no way

00:37:36.599 --> 00:37:37.639
we'll let those workers

00:37:37.639 --> 00:37:38.440
lose their money.

00:37:40.599 --> 00:37:41.960
The people's police serve the people.

00:37:42.800 --> 00:37:43.960
I'm off then.

00:37:44.039 --> 00:37:44.760
Go on.

00:37:45.400 --> 00:37:45.880
Goodbye.

00:37:51.065 --> 00:37:54.520
(Serve the People)

00:37:58.480 --> 00:37:59.599
How is Lei doing now?

00:38:06.280 --> 00:38:07.199
He is still in a coma.

00:38:07.639 --> 00:38:08.599
But the doctor said

00:38:09.480 --> 00:38:10.519
he's out of danger.

00:38:11.960 --> 00:38:13.000
I really didn't expect

00:38:13.159 --> 00:38:14.639
your mom would dare to kill someone.

00:38:15.079 --> 00:38:15.559
You know?

00:38:15.599 --> 00:38:16.639
When I went in and saw Du Lei

00:38:16.679 --> 00:38:17.480
covered in blood,

00:38:17.519 --> 00:38:18.880
I was super terrified.

00:38:19.280 --> 00:38:19.920
I was worried

00:38:19.960 --> 00:38:20.760
you'd get hurt.

00:38:22.159 --> 00:38:22.960
But thankfully,

00:38:23.639 --> 00:38:24.199
you're fine.

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:27.920
Did they find her?

00:38:57.400 --> 00:38:58.239
Captain, she is awake.

00:38:58.800 --> 00:38:59.519
Go get the doctor.

00:39:00.159 --> 00:39:00.559
Okay.

00:39:02.880 --> 00:39:03.320
Don't move!

00:39:11.599 --> 00:39:12.159
Li Jin,

00:39:13.519 --> 00:39:14.039
it's not

00:39:14.519 --> 00:39:15.760
that easy to die.

00:39:16.559 --> 00:39:17.679
Think about it carefully.

00:39:27.320 --> 00:39:28.079
The suspect

00:39:28.159 --> 00:39:29.320
cut her own wind pipe

00:39:29.320 --> 00:39:30.000
and vocal cords.

00:39:30.159 --> 00:39:31.000
The wound's been treated.

00:39:31.119 --> 00:39:32.199
But she can't speak yet.

00:39:32.679 --> 00:39:33.239
Her emotions

00:39:33.280 --> 00:39:34.280
have been unstable these days.

00:39:34.599 --> 00:39:36.079
She's been self-harming.

00:39:36.679 --> 00:39:37.639
Once she stabilizes,

00:39:37.760 --> 00:39:38.880
I'll hand her over to you.

00:39:49.280 --> 00:39:50.480
She lost control again.

00:39:50.639 --> 00:39:51.800
They just gave her a sedative.

00:39:58.735 --> 00:40:00.648
(Du Lei is awake.)

00:40:06.920 --> 00:40:07.880
If you need anything else,

00:40:07.960 --> 00:40:08.559
just let us know.

00:40:08.800 --> 00:40:09.400
Thank you.

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:10.199
I'll go back

00:40:10.199 --> 00:40:11.280
and start the transfer paperwork.

00:40:12.639 --> 00:40:13.960
This case doesn't seem complicated.

00:40:14.360 --> 00:40:15.199
It's just that

00:40:15.280 --> 00:40:17.079
the suspect
has very little will to live.

00:40:17.119 --> 00:40:18.079
That's the hard part.

00:40:19.239 --> 00:40:20.360
By the way, does she have family?

00:40:23.320 --> 00:40:23.719
Yes.

00:40:26.880 --> 00:40:27.880
Before your mom was captured,

00:40:28.119 --> 00:40:28.840
she tried to kill herself.

00:40:30.159 --> 00:40:30.840
She took a pen

00:40:30.840 --> 00:40:31.719
and stabbed her own neck

00:40:31.920 --> 00:40:32.639
several times.

00:40:34.800 --> 00:40:35.559
Don't worry.

00:40:36.199 --> 00:40:37.039
We got to her in time.

00:40:37.199 --> 00:40:38.239
She's going to be fine.

00:40:42.000 --> 00:40:43.280
How long will she get this time?

00:40:44.039 --> 00:40:45.039
That's not up to us.

00:40:45.960 --> 00:40:47.639
But what your mother did

00:40:48.119 --> 00:40:49.559
is much more serious than you think.

00:40:51.119 --> 00:40:51.840
We've already gathered

00:40:51.840 --> 00:40:52.679
key evidence.

00:40:54.280 --> 00:40:55.760
If she cooperates now,

00:40:56.039 --> 00:40:56.840
it would certainly

00:40:56.880 --> 00:40:57.880
be considered in sentencing.

00:40:59.000 --> 00:40:59.840
But she's totally

00:40:59.920 --> 00:41:00.639
shutting down

00:41:00.840 --> 00:41:01.559
and won't say anything.

00:41:02.320 --> 00:41:04.239
So could you please go see her?

00:41:49.519 --> 00:41:50.760
Just confess to the police.

00:41:56.039 --> 00:41:57.079
If you cooperate,

00:41:58.360 --> 00:42:00.559
there might be a chance for leniency.

00:42:03.599 --> 00:42:04.679
Do you remember?

00:42:06.239 --> 00:42:07.360
When I was very little,

00:42:08.599 --> 00:42:10.119
once you took me to the amusement park.

00:42:11.920 --> 00:42:13.480
Your smile was really beautiful
at that time.

00:42:14.760 --> 00:42:16.000
And I was always

00:42:17.159 --> 00:42:17.840
clinging to you.

00:42:19.320 --> 00:42:20.719
That day, a float on the street

00:42:21.239 --> 00:42:22.000
was broken.

00:42:24.239 --> 00:42:25.440
When it fell towards me,

00:42:27.280 --> 00:42:28.360
I thought I was done for.

00:42:30.000 --> 00:42:31.159
But when I opened my eyes,

00:42:32.239 --> 00:42:33.239
I saw your face.

00:42:34.400 --> 00:42:35.719
You protected me under your body,

00:42:36.559 --> 00:42:37.199
but your hands

00:42:38.000 --> 00:42:39.320
and body were covered in blood.

00:42:40.559 --> 00:42:41.719
Before the ambulance came,

00:42:42.480 --> 00:42:43.840
you held me so tight.

00:42:45.719 --> 00:42:46.440
You told me,

00:42:48.480 --> 00:42:49.079
"Nuo,

00:42:50.480 --> 00:42:51.079
it's okay.

00:42:52.760 --> 00:42:53.320
Don't be afraid.

00:42:54.519 --> 00:42:55.079
Don't be afraid."

00:42:57.000 --> 00:42:58.280
I can never forget

00:42:59.960 --> 00:43:01.079
that warmth in my life.

00:43:05.080 --> 00:43:07.880
(Next Episode)

00:43:08.159 --> 00:43:09.400
(Actress, Ren Suxi)
I'm Ren Suxi.

00:43:09.559 --> 00:43:11.440
(Actress, Ren Suxi)
I invite you to watch Wonder Wall.

00:43:11.719 --> 00:43:13.039
We should sell the place

00:43:13.039 --> 00:43:13.559
as soon as possible.

00:43:13.800 --> 00:43:15.440
The 1.02 million owed to Hong Jinkui

00:43:16.000 --> 00:43:16.760
should be paid back.

00:43:17.119 --> 00:43:18.360
Agreed.

00:43:18.559 --> 00:43:19.440
How much is the deposit?

00:43:19.599 --> 00:43:20.239
Five percent.

00:43:20.360 --> 00:43:21.280
225 thousand.

00:43:21.280 --> 00:43:21.880
Round it up

00:43:21.880 --> 00:43:22.400
to 300 thousand.

